OL,3,CDaniel Khalife 'thought British
OL,4,Csecurity services would be impressed
OL,5,Cwith him'
OL,7,FFormer British soldier, Daniel
OL,8,FKhalife, who is accused of passing
OL,9,Fsecret information to Iran, thought
OL,10,FBritish security services would be
OL,11,F"impressed" with him after he covertly
OL,12,Fgathered the names of special forces
OL,13,Fpersonnel, his trial has heard.
OL,15,FDaniel Khalife, 23, told Woolwich
OL,16,FCrown Court he was "surprised" when he
OL,17,Fdiscovered a "flaw" in an internal HR
OL,18,Fsystem for booking leave, allowing him
OL,19,Fto find further details about the
OL,20,Fsoldiers on a promotions list in 2021.
