OL,3,CDaniel Khalife 'thought British
OL,4,Csecurity services would be impressed
OL,5,Cwith him'
OL,7,FHe took a photo of a handwritten list
OL,8,Fof 15 soldiers, including some serving
OL,9,Fin the Special Air Service and Special
OL,10,FBoat Service, the court was told
OL,11,Fpreviously.
OL,13,FProsecutors claim Khalife was paid in
OL,14,Fcash by the Iranian intelligence
OL,15,Fservice for secret information
OL,16,Fgathered during his time in the Army.
