OL,3,CDaniel Khalife 'thought British
OL,4,Csecurity services would be impressed
OL,5,Cwith him'
OL,7,FKhalife said he was worried about
OL,8,Fbeing "ignored again" by the security
OL,9,Fservices, and wanted to prove he was
OL,10,Fsomeone with "access" to important
OL,11,Fmaterial.
OL,13,FHe said: "I wanted to be given the
OL,14,Fopportunity to explain myself. I have
OL,15,Falways had a gift for exposing flaws
OL,16,Fin security. I was the only person in
OL,17,Fthe Ministry of Defence who discovered
OL,18,Fthis flaw."
