OL,3,CDaniel Khalife 'thought British
OL,4,Csecurity services would be impressed
OL,5,Cwith him'
OL,7,FGiving evidence at the court earlier
OL,8,Ftoday, Daniel Khalife said he wanted
OL,9,Fto "draw out" the Iranian intelligence
OL,10,Fofficers he was in touch with and
OL,11,F"strengthen the relationship based on
OL,12,Flies".
OL,14,FThe 23-year-old told jurors he
OL,15,F"considered potentially travelling to
OL,16,FIran" while still a serving soldier,
OL,17,Fbut feared there could be consequences
OL,18,Fif they found out the information he
OL,19,Fwas providing was "fictitious".
