OL,3,CDaniel Khalife 'thought British
OL,4,Csecurity services would be impressed
OL,5,Cwith him'
OL,7,F"I felt this would be dangerous," he
OL,8,Fsaid.
OL,10,FWhen police arrested him and searched
OL,11,Fhis room, they found a number of
OL,12,F"completely fake" documents purporting
OL,13,Fto be from MPs, senior military
OL,14,Fofficials and the security services,
OL,15,Fhis trial heard previously.
OL,17,FKhalife told the court he thought up a
OL,18,Fplan to "digitise" the documents, by
OL,19,Fputting a laptop in a "fake diplomatic
OL,20,Fbag" to make it seem like it had been
OL,21,Fintercepted.
