OL,4,Csecurity services would be impressed
OL,5,Cwith him'
OL,7,FHe intended to try and sell the
OL,8,Fdevice, jurors heard.
OL,10,FAsked about the use of WhatsApp groups
OL,11,Fto share orders and even secret
OL,12,Fdocuments in the army, Khalife said
OL,13,Fthe practice was "standard procedure",
OL,14,Fadding that it would be "impossible"
OL,15,Fto operate without it.
