OL,3,CDaniel Khalife 'thought British
OL,4,Csecurity services would be impressed
OL,5,Cwith him'
OL,7,FThe former soldier is alleged to have
OL,8,Ffled his army barracks in January 2023
OL,9,Fwhen he realised he would face
OL,10,Fcriminal charges over allegations he
OL,11,Fpassed classified information to
OL,12,FIran's intelligence service.
OL,14,FLater, while on remand, he is alleged
OL,15,Fto have escaped from HMP Wandsworth in
OL,16,FSeptember 2023 by tying himself to the
OL,17,Funderside of a food delivery truck
OL,18,Fusing bedsheets.
