OL,5,Cwith him'
OL,7,FAs well as the prison escape, he also
OL,8,Ffaces charges contrary to the Official
OL,9,FSecrets Act and Terrorism Act, and is
OL,10,Faccused of perpetrating a bomb hoax.
OL,12,FHe denies all the charges, and the
OL,13,Ftrial continues.
